From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Damon Lynch <damonlynch@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 26 Jan 2026 16:52:42 +1300
Subject: [PATCH] Fix #261 sqlite3.OperationalError: unable to open database
 file

Fix failure to close database connections that creates a runtime
error under Python 3.14.

(cherry picked from commit 1c26115136d23cf63ac498bc2deaa9fbcac7d8e5)
